Interface DetectionAlgorithm

All Superinterfaces:
Activatible, java.util.concurrent.Callable<FrameworkTask>, FrameworkTask, FullyInitializable, Initializable, Learnable
All Known Implementing Classes:
BasicDetectionAlgorithm, MultipleDetectionAlgorithm
public interface DetectionAlgorithm
extends FrameworkTask

A process which detects a pattern (feature) in SensoryMemory content and excites PamNodes representing that pattern.

Author:
Javier Snaider, Ryan J. McCall
